## 6. MATCHMAKING LOGIC (CRITICAL)

### Requirements

* Do NOT serve purely random matchups
* Do NOT always show top fragrances

### Basic Rules

* 60%: Match fragrances with similar Elo
* 25%: Force potential upsets (lower vs higher)
* 15%: Popular vs obscure

Avoid repeat pairings within a short session.

---

## 7. RANKING SYSTEM

### Scoring

* Use **Elo rating system**
* Separate Elo per arena
* Rankings are derived from Elo (not raw vote count)

### Visibility

* Elo is hidden
* Rank position is public
* Rank movement shown post-vote

